<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Email Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #003366 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: white;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background: #F9FAFB;
      border: 2px dashed #E5E7EB;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #003366;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #F9FAFB;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6B7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎉 Welcome to VeriPoint!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hi there,</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
        Thank you for signing up for VeriPoint, Babcock University's official attendance system. Please use the verification code below to complete your registration:
      </p>
      
      <div class="otp-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280;">Your Verification Code</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9CA3AF;">
          This code will expire in 15 minutes
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280;">
        If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2026 VeriPoint. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
